    "Edwardes et al. (2024) emphasize the importance of quantifying the trade-offs between precision livestock farming technologies and conventional welfare improvements, particularly in areas such as mobility management for dairy cattle (120).",
    "The break-even point for HACI technologies varies by farm size and operational type.",
    "For instance, Kimmerer et al.",
